{{!--
    Global Template: Einstein Decisions

    This Global Template inserts a Promotion, chosen by an Einstein Decision (Contextual Bandit).

    Requirements:
    1) Set the content zone(s) to that defined in your Sitemap.
    2) Ensure that the "Contextual Bandit" feature flag is enabled for your account. If you encounter issues,
    please contact your account administrator.
    3) Ensure that the "Feature Engineering" features (Einstein Decisions > Feature Engineering) are enabled
    for the dataset. Once again, please contact your account administrator if you encounter issues.
    4) Enable Promotions in the dataset's Catalog Setup.
    5) Create and configure Promotions, either manually or through an ETL.

    Customizations:
    1) Remove or change the default value for maxResults in Serverside Code.
--}}

{{#if promotion}}
<div id="evg-einstein-decisions" data-evg-campaign-id="{{campaign}}"
data-evg-experience-id="{{experience}}" data-evg-user-group="{{userGroup}}">
    <a class="evg-promotion-link" href="{{promotion.attributes.url.value}}">
        <img class="evg-promotion-img" src="{{promotion.assets.[0].imageUrl}}"
        alt-text="{{promotion.attributes.name.value}}">
    </a>
</div>
{{/if}}
